Peter Jones ya yi "hargitsi" bayan Holly Willoughby ta janye daga yarjejeniyar fam miliyan 11
Tauraruwar 'yan wasan Dragons Peter Jones ya yi "hargitsi" bayan da Holly Willoughby ta janye daga yarjejeniyar £11m da ta yi da alamar salon rayuwarta domin mayar da hankali kan sabbin kwangilolin da ta yi da Marks and Spencer da ITV
Willoughby ba shi da lokacin da za su yi amfani da kayayyakin gida da na kayan ado na Truly.
An kwatanta kamfanin da Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop.
Mai gabatar da shirin This Morning, mai shekara 37, ta shiga shafin Instagram ta sanar da cewa ta bar aikin.
Holly Willoughby ta bar Peter Jones, dan wasan kungiyar Dragons, cikin fushi bayan ta janye daga kasuwancin su na rayuwa a minti na karshe domin mayar da hankali kan sabbin kwangilar ta da Marks & Spencer da ITV.
Majiyoyi sun ce Jones ya yi "fushi" lokacin da shahararren mai watsa shirye-shirye a wani taro mai cike da tashin hankali a ranar Talata a hedkwatar kasuwancinsa a Marlow a Buckinghamshire, cewa sabbin yarjejeniyoyinsa  masu darajar har zuwa fam miliyan 1.5  sun nuna cewa ba ta da isasshen lokaci don kayayyakin gida da kayan haɗi na Truly.
An kwatanta kamfanin da Gwyneth Paltrow's Goop kuma an yi hasashen cewa zai ninka dukiyar Willoughby da aka kiyasta na fam miliyan 11.
Willoughby, mai shekara 37, ta shiga shafin Instagram ta sanar da cewa ta bar Truly, yayin da Jones ya tashi daga Burtaniya zuwa daya daga cikin wuraren hutu.
Wani majiya ya ce: "Gaskiya ta kasance ɗaya daga cikin abubuwan da Holly ta fi so.
Wannan aikin na dogon lokaci ne da za ta yi a cikin shekaru da yawa masu zuwa.
Ƙudurin da ta yi na janyewa ya ba kowa mamaki.
Ba wanda zai yarda da abin da ya faru a ranar Talata, sa'ad da muke gab da kaddamar da jirgin.
Akwai ɗakunan ajiya da ke cike da kayayyaki a hedkwatarmu da ke Marlow, kuma an riga an shirya su don sayarwa".
Masana sun ce, sauka daga gidan tallar The Morning, wadda ke cikin taurari masu samun kuɗi mafi yawa a Burtaniya, na iya jawo wa kamfanin asarar miliyoyin daloli saboda yawan saka hannun jari a kayayyakin  daga matashin kai zuwa kyandir zuwa tufafi da kayayyakin gida  da kuma yiwuwar ƙarin jinkiri a kaddamar da shi.
Kuma hakan zai iya kawo ƙarshen abokantaka na dogon lokaci.
Mahaifiyar 'ya'ya uku, Willoughby, da kuma mai gidan Dan Baldwin sun kasance suna da dangantaka ta kusa da Jones da matarsa Tara Capp na shekaru goma.
Willoughby ya kafa Truly tare da Capp a 2016, kuma Jones, 52, ya shiga matsayin shugaban kwamitin a watan Maris.
Ma'aurata biyu suna hutu tare, kuma Jones yana da kashi 40 cikin 100 na kamfanin samar da talabijin na Baldwin.
Willoughby zai zama jakadan wuta na M&S kuma zai maye gurbin Ant McPartlin a matsayin mai gabatar da shirin I'm A Celebrity na ITV.
Wani majiya da ke kusa da Jones ya ce a daren jiya, "Ba za mu iya yin sharhi kan ayyukansa na kasuwanci ba".
"Kuma sai muka yi soyayya"
Ya yi dariya game da sukar da zai samu daga kafafen yada labarai saboda yin tsokaci da ya ce "bai dace da shugaban kasa ba" da kuma nuna irin wannan amincewa ga shugaban Koriya ta Arewa.
Me ya sa Shugaba Trump ya yi watsi da abubuwa da yawa?
Trump ya ce a cikin wani jawabinsa na satar labarai.
"Ban yi watsi da kome ba".
