Sama da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli sauraron Brett Kavanaugh
Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidar da aka bayar a ranar Alhamis daga wanda aka zabi a matsayin babban alkalin kotun kasar Brett Kavanaugh da kuma matar da ta zarge shi da laifin cin zarafin da ake zargin ya faru a shekarun 1980s, Christine Blasey Ford, a tashoshin talabijin shida.
A lokaci guda, an ci gaba da fafutukar siyasa da tashoshin watsa labarai suka katse shirye-shiryen su na yau da kullum domin su sanar da abubuwan da suka faru a ranar Juma'a: yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya kafa, wanda ya ba wa FBI damar gudanar da bincike na mako guda kan zargin.
Ford ta shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa ta tabbata cewa Kavanaugh ya sha giya ya yi mata ta'aziyya, ya kuma yi kokarin cire mata tufafinta don zuwa wani biki na makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh ya ce a cikin wata sanarwa da ya bayar, yana da tabbacin cewa hakan bai faru ba.
Nielsen ya ce mutane miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli bidiyon a ranar Jumma'a.
Kamfanin ya ba da rahoton matsakaicin yawan masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Babu wasu 'yan kallo da aka samu nan take daga wasu tashoshin da suka nuna hakan, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Nielsen kuma tana da matsala wajen auna yawan masu kallon shirye-shirye a ofisoshi.
Don a kwatanta, wannan adadin ya yi daidai da na wasan da ake yi a gasar cin kofin duniya ko kuma gasar Oscars.
Kamfanin Fox News Channel, wanda masu gabatar da ra'ayoyinsa suka goyi bayan nadin Kavanaugh, ya kasance a saman dukkan tashoshi da matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a lokacin sauraron da ya dauki tsawon yini, in ji Nielsen.
ABC ce ta biyu da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
CBS tana da miliyan 3.1 da NBC tana da miliyan 2.94 da MSNBC tana da miliyan 2.89 da CNN tana da miliyan 2.52 a cewar Nielsen.
Sha'awa ta kasance mai yawa bayan taron.
Flake shi ne babban dan wasan da aka yi a ranar Juma'a.
Bayan ofishin jam'iyyar moderate Republican ya fitar da sanarwa cewa zai zabi Kavanaugh, an kama shi a yayin da aka bude kyamarorin CNN da CBS a safiyar Juma'a yayin da masu zanga-zanga suka yi masa ihu yayin da yake kokarin hawa wani lif zuwa wurin sauraron kwamitin shari'a.
Ya tsaya yana kallon ƙasa na mintuna da yawa yayin da ake yi masa ba'a, kuma CNN tana watsa shi kai tsaye.
"Ina tsaye a gabanka", in ji wata mata.
"Kana ganin yana gaya wa ƙasar gaskiya?"
An gaya masa cewa, "Kana da iko sosai, kuma mata da yawa ba su da iko".
Flake ya ce ofishinsa ya fitar da wata sanarwa, kuma ya ce kafin a rufe lif, yana son ya kara da cewa a lokacin da aka yi zaman kwamitin.
Dukan tashoshin talabijin sun watsa labaransa a kai a kai bayan 'yan sa'o'i kaɗan, lokacin da kwamitin shari'a ya yi zaɓe a kan ko za a ci gaba da zaɓen Kavanaugh zuwa ga dukan majalisar dattawa.
Amma Flake ya ce zai kada kuri'ar ne kawai a kan imanin cewa FBI za ta bincika tuhumar da ake yi wa dan takarar a mako mai zuwa, abin da 'yan Democrat da ke da rinjaye a majalisar dattawa suka bukaci.
Flake ya yi imani da wani abu ne daga tattaunawar da ya yi da abokinsa, Sanata Chris Coons na jam'iyyar Democrat.
Bayan tattaunawa da Coons da wasu sanatoci bayan haka, Flake ya yanke shawarar.
Zaɓin Flake ya yi tasiri, domin ya bayyana cewa 'yan Republican ba za su sami kuri'un amincewa da Kavanaugh ba tare da binciken ba.
Shugaba Trump ya bude wani bincike na FBI kan zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh.
