Livingston mai ci ya yi wa Rangers biris, inda ya ci Steven Gerrard kashi na biyu bayan wasanni 18 a matsayin kocin Ibrox.
Wasan Dolly Menga ya kawo canji, sa'ad da 'yan wasan Gary Holt suka ci gaba da tsayawa a gaba tare da Hibernian a matsayi na biyu.
Kungiyar Gerrard ba ta samu nasara a gasar zakarun Turai ba a wannan kakar kuma za ta kara da Hearts wadda ke kan gaba da su da maki takwas a gaba a ranar Lahadi.
A lokacin, Rangers za su ziyarci Rapid Vienna a gasar Europa League a ranar Alhamis.
Livingston dai na karawa kungiyarsa nasara a wasanni shida, kuma kocin kungiyar Holt bai taba samun rashin nasara ba tun lokacin da ya maye gurbin Kenny Miller a watan da ya gabata.
Livingston ya yi watsi da damar da yake da ita na cin nasara
Ya kamata 'yan wasan Holt su kasance a gaba tun kafin su ci kwallo, kuma yadda suke wasa ya jawo wa Rangers matsala.
Scott Robinson ya shiga, amma ya bayar da shi a gaban raga, sa'annan Alan Lithgow ya buga a waje da raga, bayan ya yi tsalle don buga Craig Halkett a gaban raga.
'Yan wasan gida sun yarda su bar Rangers su yi wasa a gabansu domin sun san cewa za su iya kawo wa tawagar matsala a lokacin da suka yi kasa.
Kuma a cikin wannan yanayi ne babban burin ya zo.
Rangers sun buga kwallo, Livingston ya yi amfani da wani bude, Declan Gallagher da Robinson sun hada kai don samar da wasan zuwa Menga, wanda ya yi taɓawa kuma ya zira kwallaye daga tsakiyar filin.
A wannan lokacin, Rangers sun mamaye kwallon amma suna fama da samun damar shiga cikin tsaron gida, kuma mai tsaron raga Liam Kelly ba shi da kalubale.
Wannan yanayin ya ci gaba a karo na biyu, duk da cewa Alfredo Morelos ya hana Kelly ceto.
Scott Pittman ya yi nasara da ƙwallon ƙafa na Rangers Allan McGregor, kuma Lithgow ya yi nasara a waje da frame a wani yanayi na Livingston.
An ci gaba da yin wasannin da aka yi a filin Livingston, amma an hana su, kuma an ƙi buƙatun fansa biyu  bayan Halkett ya kama mai maye gurbin Glenn Middleton da ɗaya don hannun a kan kwallon .
