Birnin yana da yawan Turkawa mafi yawa a wajen Turkiyya.
'Yan sanda sun hana mutane 25,000 taruwa a gaban masallacin saboda dalilai na tsaro, amma masu goyon baya da dama sun zo kusa don ganin shugaban kasar.
Daruruwan 'yan adawar Erdogan  da yawa daga cikinsu Kurdawa  ma sun lura kuma sun la'anci manufofin Erdogan da kuma shawarar gwamnatin Jamus ta karɓi baƙi a ƙasar.
Wannan zanga-zanga ta nuna wani baƙo mai rikici wanda wasu Turkawa na Jamus ke ganinsa a matsayin gwarzo, wasu kuma suna yi masa ba'a a matsayin mai mulkin kama karya.
