Wani dan rapper Kanye West ya canza sunansa zuwa Ye.
Ya sanar da sauyin a ranar Asabar a shafinsa na Twitter inda ya rubuta, "Halitta da aka sani da Kanye West".
West, mai shekara 41, ya yi amfani da sunan Ye na ɗan lokaci kuma ya yi amfani da sunan a matsayin taken album na takwas, wanda aka fitar a watan Yuni.
Wannan canjin ya faru ne kafin fitowar sa a shirin Saturday Night Live, inda ake sa ran zai fitar da sabon album dinsa na Yandhi.
Ya maye gurbin mawaƙa Ariana Grande a wasan kwaikwayon, wanda ya soke saboda "dalilai na motsin rai", in ji mai gabatar da wasan kwaikwayon.
