Taron zaben Trump a jihar West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara taron zaben da aka yi a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko cikin tarurrukan Trump biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da tarurruka a wurare masu goyon bayan Trump kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da aka dakatar da zaben tabbatar da alƙalin da Trump ya nada don zama a babban kotun, Trump yana ƙoƙarin samar da goyon baya ga zaɓen da ke tafe saboda 'yan Republican suna fuskantar haɗarin rasa ikon majalisa lokacin da aka kada kuri'a a watan Nuwamba.
Yaushe ne taron Trump a yammacin Virginia a daren yau, kuma yaya kake ganin hakan a kan layi?
Za a gudanar da taron Trump a garin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia da tsakar dare tsakanin ranar Asabar, 29 ga watan Nuwamba, da kuma Lahadi, 30 ga watan Nuwamba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia ta hanyar YouTube.
Trump zai yi magana ne a kan sauraron da za a yi a wannan makon game da Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka nada a matsayin babban alkalin kotun, wanda ya yi ta fama da tashin hankali sakamakon zargin cin zarafin mata, kuma an dakatar da kuri'ar amincewa da majalisar dattawa da ake sa ran za ta yi a mako guda, yayin da FBI ke binciken tuhumar.
Amma babban dalilin da ya sa ake gudanar da wannan taron shi ne don a ba da gudummawa ga 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar babban zabe a watan Nuwamba.
Masu yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump sun ce, taron zabe guda biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, na nufin "karfafawa masu sa kai da masu goyon baya a yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma kara yawan rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da na wakilai", in ji Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisa na da muhimmanci ga ajandar shugaban kasa, don haka shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da dama a lokacin da muke shiga lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun Trump, wanda bai so a ambaci sunansa ba, a Reuters.
Za a gudanar da taron zaben na yau da dare a filin wasa na Wesbanco a birnin Wheeling, kuma ana sa ran za a samu 'yan jam'iyyar Trump daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma kafofin yada labarai daga Pittsburgh", in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar, Trump ya kai ziyara karo na biyu a watan jiya a jihar West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin 100 a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican na West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke baya a zaben.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya yi gaggawar samun ci gaba a zabensa ba", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a jami'ar West Virginia, kamar yadda Reuters ta ruwaito.
