Rangers sun sake shan kaye a filin wasa, lokacin da Dolly Menga ta ci kwallo, wanda ya sa Steven Gerrard ya ci 1-0 a Livingston.
Kungiyar Ibrox ta nemi nasarar farko a kan hanya tun bayan nasarar 4-1 da suka yi a St Johnstone a watan Fabrairu, amma kungiyar Gary Holt ta ba Gerrard kashi na biyu a wasanni 18 a matsayin kocin, inda suka kai Hearts maki takwas a matsayin na farko a gasar Ladbrokes.
