Game of Thrones star Kit Harington yana neman ya zama mai yawan sha'awar maza
Kit Harington sananne ne saboda rawar da ya taka a matsayin Jon Snow a cikin wasan kwaikwayo na HBO mai ban tsoro na wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo.
Amma ɗan wasan mai shekaru 31 ya yi watsi da halin jarumin, ya ce irin waɗannan halayen suna sa matasa maza su ji cewa suna bukatar su yi ƙarfi don a daraja su.
Kit ya shaida wa Sunday Times Culture cewa yana ganin "wani abu ya ɓace" kuma ya tambayi yadda za a magance matsalar ƙarancin maza a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda kwanan nan ya auri 'yar wasan kwaikwayon Game of Thrones, Rose Leslie, a shekara 31, ya yarda cewa matsalar tana "tunaninsa sosai".
"A halin yanzu, abin da ke damuna sosai shi ne, 'Ina ne muka yi kuskure a cikin gari game da namiji?'", in ji shi.
"Idan muka duba matsalolin da muke fuskanta yanzu, menene muka koya wa matasa a lokacin da suke girma?"
Kit ya yi imanin cewa talabijin na iya zama wani ɓangare na haɓaka na masculinity mai guba saboda ƙimar maza.
Ya ci gaba: "Me aka haifa, kuma menene aka koya?
Menene matasa maza suke koya daga talabijin da kuma kan titi da ke sa su ji cewa dole ne su zama maza a wannan hanyar?
Ina tsammanin wannan babbar tambaya ce ta zamaninmu  yaya zamu canza hakan?
Domin a bayyane yake cewa wani abu ya faru da waɗannan samari".
A cikin hirar, ya kuma yarda cewa ba zai yi wani abin da zai biyo bayan Game of Thrones ba lokacin da wasan ya ƙare a bazara mai zuwa, yana mai cewa "ya gama da fagen fama da dawakai".
Kit ya shiga fim a watan Nuwamba na fim din Sam Shepard mai suna True West, wanda ya shafi wani darakta da kuma dan'uwansa da ya yi sata.
A kwanan nan, ɗan wasan ya bayyana cewa yana ganin saduwa da matarsa Rose shine mafi kyawun kwarewar Game of Thrones.
"Na sadu da matata ne saboda wannan shirin, kuma ta haka ta ba ni iyali na nan gaba kuma ta tsara rayuwata har abada", in ji shi.
Rose ta buga Ygritte, wanda halin Kit, Jon Snow, ya ƙaunace shi, a cikin kyautar Emmy Award-winning fantasy series.
Ma'auratan sun yi aure a watan Yunin 2018 a gidan Leslie a Scotland.
HIV/AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton ƙaruwar sabbin cututtuka da kashi 14
Kasar Sin ta sanar da karuwar yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da kuma cutar kanjamau da kashi 14 cikin dari.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 a ƙasar ne suka kamu, in ji hukumar kiwon lafiya.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai, an sami sabbin mutane 40,000.
Mafi yawan sababbin cututtuka sun kasance ana iya samun su ta hanyar jima'i, wanda sabon abu ne.
A al'adance, cutar HIV ta yadu cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin ta hanyar kamuwa da jini.
Amma adadin mutanen da suke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro a lardin Yunnan.
Amma a cikin shekara guda, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar HIV da AIDS a China ya ƙaru da 100,000.
Cutar HIV da ake yadawa ta hanyar jima'i, babbar matsala ce a cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin.
An halatta luwadi a shekara ta 1997, amma ana zargin cewa nuna bambanci ga mutanen da suke da jinsi ɗaya ya zama ruwan dare gama gari.
Bincike ya nuna cewa kashi 70 zuwa 90 bisa ɗari na maza da suke yin jima'i da maza suna yin aure da mata a wani lokaci domin ƙa'idodin ƙasarsu na ra'ayin mazan jiya.
Yawancin cututtuka suna faruwa ne saboda rashin amfani da maganin hana haihuwa a waɗannan yanayi.
Tun 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi alkawarin samun magani kyauta da daidaito don magance matsalar cutar HIV.
Maxine Waters ta musanta cewa ma'aikatanta sun fitar da bayanan 'yan majalisar dattijai na Republican kuma ta yi tir da "karya mai haɗari" da kuma "ra'ayoyin maƙarƙashiya".
A ranar Asabar, 'yar majalisar wakilai Maxine Waters ta musanta zargin cewa wani ma'aikaciyarta ta raba bayanan sirri na wasu 'yan majalisar wakilai uku a shafin Wikipedia.
Dan Democrat na Los Angeles ya yi ikirarin cewa, waɗannan zarge-zargen sun fito ne daga shafukan yanar gizo da kuma masu goyon bayan "yancin-kai".
"Ƙarya, ƙarya, da kuma wasu munanan ƙarya", in ji Waters a shafinsa na Twitter.
An ce bayanan da aka fitar sun ƙunshi adireshin gida da kuma lambobin waya na 'yan majalisar dattawa Lindsey Graham na jihar South Carolina da Mike Lee da Orrin Hatch, waɗanda suke Utah.
An wallafa wannan bayanin ne a ranar Alhamis, a wani shafin yanar gizo da ba a san ko wane ne ba a Capitol Hill, a lokacin da ake gudanar da zaman majalisar dattawa game da zargin cin zarafin da aka yi wa Brett Kavanaugh, wanda shi ne dan takarar kotun koli.
An samu wannan bayanan ne bayan da wasu 'yan majalisar dattijai uku suka yi wa Kavanaugh tambayoyi.
Shafukan tallafi na masu ra'ayin mazan jiya kamar su Gateway Pundit of RedState sun sanar da cewa adiresoshin IP ɗin sun nuna cewa mutanen Waters ne suka sanya bayanan, sannan suka fitar da bayanan wani memba na ma'aikatan Waters, in ji The Hill.
"Wannan zargi ba shi da tushe kuma ƙarya ce ta kai tsaye", in ji Waters.
"Mambobin ma'aikatana, wanda aka yi wa karya a cikin mutuncinsa, da kuma bayanansa, da kuma amincinsa sakamakon waɗannan zarge-zargen na yaudara da ƙarya, ba su da alhakin wannan ɓarnar bayanai.
Wannan zargi da ba shi da tushe ba gaskiya ne kuma ƙarya ce ta gaskiya".
Waters ya yi saurin samun suka a shafukan intanet, ciki har da tsohon sakataren yada labarai na fadar White House Ari Fleischer.
"Wannan ƙin yarda ne mai tsanani", in ji Fleischer.
"Wannan ya nuna cewa ba ta da halin da ya dace ta zama 'yar majalisa.
Idan aka zarge ka da wani abin da ba ka yi ba, kada ka yi fushi.
Kada ka yi rashin biyayya.
Kada ka yi shakkar dalilin da ya sa mai tuhumar ya yi hakan.
Dole ne mutum ya kasance da kwanciyar hankali".
Fleischer ya kwatanta yadda Waters ya amsa da sukar da 'yan Democrat suka yi wa Kavanaugh, wanda aka zargi da yin fushi a zaman kotun na ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navarro, dan takarar Republican da ke neman maye gurbin Waters a zaben tsakiyar shekara, ya kuma bayyana ra'ayinsa a shafinsa na Twitter.
"Babban abu idan gaskiya ne", in ji shi.
A cikin sanarwar Waters, ta ce ma'aikatanta sun tuntubi "hukumomi da hukumomin tsaro da suka dace game da wadannan zarge-zargen".
"Za mu tabbatar da cewa an sami masu laifin", ta ci gaba. "Za a kuma hukunta su saboda ayyukansu da suke da lahani da kuma haɗari ga kowa da kowa a cikin ma'aikatata".
Johnny English ya sake yin fim mai ban dariya mai suna Rowan Atkinson
Ya zama al'ada a nemi wani bangare na Brexit a duk wani sabon fim da ke nuna wani ɗan Burtaniya, kuma hakan ya zama daidai da sabon wasan kwaikwayo na wasan kwaikwayo na Johnny English, wanda ya fara a 2003 tare da Johnny English kuma ya sake bayyana a 2011 tare da Johnny English - haifaffen sake.
Za a yi wa'azi da ba'a game da yadda muke da matsala, don zama sabon fitar da kayayyaki na ƙasar?
A'a, Johnny English, wanda ba shi da basira, mai fuska mai laushi da manyan idanu, ya sami izinin yin baƙar magana a sake, sunansa ya nuna fiye da komai cewa shi mai ban dariya ne wanda ya yi niyya ga wuraren da masu zuwa cinema ba sa jin Turanci.
Shi ne, ba shakka, mai ba da labari na sirri wanda, duk da sha'awarsa na zama mai ladabi, yana da ɗan Clouseau, Mr. Bean mai kaifi da kuma kyakkyawan kullun da ya yi wa waƙa guda ɗaya na Chariots of Fire a bikin bude gasar Olympics ta London ta 2012.
Ya kuma samo asali ne daga duniya da kuma na kasa da kasa mai suna Lousebrook, wanda ya bar rikici a cikin sawunsa bayan Atkinson ya nuna shi a cikin tallan talabijin na Barclaycard.
Akwai wasu abubuwa masu kyau a wannan sabon harbi na JE.
Ina son ganin Johnny English yana zuwa da wani jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu da yake sanye da makamai na zamanin da kuma na'urar da ke motsa jirgin tana ratsa kan kwalkwali.
Za ka iya ganin baiwar Atkinson na yin wasan kwaikwayo na zahiri, amma abin dariya yana jin daɗi sosai kuma ba shi da amfani, musamman ma a yanzu da fina-finai masu "mai tsanani" kamar 007 da Mission Impossible suna ba da labari mai gamsarwa a matsayin kayan haɗi.
Abin dariya ya fi mayar da hankali ga yara fiye da manya, kuma a ganina, irin wannan baƙon abin mamaki na Johnny English ba shi da ƙwarewa da kuma mayar da hankali kamar yadda Atkinson ya yi a fim din fim din Mr. Bean.
Abin da ya fi muhimmanci a fim shi ne cewa ƙasar Ingila tana cikin mawuyacin hali.
Wani dan dandalin intanet ya shiga cikin manyan cibiyoyin leken asirin Ingila, ya bayyana sunayen duk wani dan Birtaniya da ke cikin filin, abin takaici ga dan wasan da ke da alhakin, amma abin takaici, Kevin Eldon bai taka rawa ba.
Wannan shi ne na karshe ga wani Firayim Minista mai girman kai da kuma mai son yaki, wanda ya riga ya sha wahala daga cikakken raguwa a cikin shahararren siyasa: Emma Thompson yana yin mafi kyau tare da wannan hali mai kama da Teresa May, amma babu wani abu da za a yi a rubutun.
Da yake masu ba ta shawara a kan tsaro sun gaya mata cewa an gano kowane ɗan leƙen asiri da ke aiki a cikinta, sai ta soma hana wasu daga cikin ma'aikatanta samun kuɗin fansho.
Kuma, ba shakka, Johnny English ne, wanda yanzu shi ne mai kula da makarantar sakandare, amma yana koyar da yadda za a zama jami'in ɓoye. Akwai wasu abubuwa masu ban sha'awa a nan, inda English yake da irin wannan horo na makarantar Rock a fannin leken asiri.
English ya koma taron gaggawa a Whitehall kuma ya sake haduwa da tsohon dan wasan da ya sha wahala Bough, wanda Ben Miller ya sake buga shi.
Bough yanzu ya auri wani kyaftin din jirgin ruwa mai son zuciya amma mai son zuciya - rawar da Vicki Pepperdine ke takawa.
Saboda haka, batman da Robin sun dawo daga cikin ayyukan sirri na sarauta lokacin da suka sadu da Olga Kurylenko mai ban mamaki femme fatale, Ophilia Bulletova.
A halin yanzu, Firayim Minista yana gab da shiga cikin karamar hukumar da mai karamar fasahar zamani Jason Volta - wanda Jake Lacy ya buga - wanda ke da'awar cewa zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Ingila.
English da Bough sun fara haɗarin haɗarin haɗari: suna yin kama da masu hidima suna ƙone wani babban gidan cin abinci na Faransa; suna haifar da rikici yayin da suke shiga cikin jirgin jirgin ruwan Volta; kuma English ya kirkiro ragnarok mai tsabta yayin da yake ƙoƙarin amfani da tabarau na gaskiya don sanin gidan Volta.
An harba dukan bindigogi a ƙarshen fim ɗin, amma ko da yake yana da kyau kuma yana da ƙarfi, yana da kamar yadda yara suke kallon talabijin.
Abin da ya fi muni.
Kuma kamar yadda na yi tunani a kan sauran fina-finai na Johnny English, shin masana'antar fim ta Ingila ba za ta iya ba Rowan Atkinson wani matsayi da zai yi daidai da baiwarsa ba?
Ma'aikatan Labour sun ki amincewa da shirin samar da hutun kwana hudu a mako, ba tare da an sauya albashi ba ga 'yan Birtaniya
An ce jam'iyyar Jeremy Corbyn ta Labour tana tunanin wani tsari na musamman, wanda zai sa 'yan Ingila su gamsu da aikin kwana hudu amma su samu albashin kwana biyar.
Jam'iyyar ta ce za ta so shugabannin kamfanoni su yi amfani da tanadin da suka samu daga fasaha ta wucin gadi (AI) don ba ma'aikata karin ranar hutu.
Hakan zai sa ma'aikatan su yi hutu na kwana uku ba tare da rage albashi ba.
Majiyoyi sun ce ra'ayin zai yi daidai da burin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar na tura kasar cikin hanyar da ta fi dacewa ga ma'aikata.
Taron Tarayyar Tarayyar Tarayya na goyon bayan ra'ayin ranar aiki ta kwana huɗu a matsayin hanyar da ma'aikata za su amfana daga canjin tattalin arziki.
Wani babban dan jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa The Sunday Times cewa: "Ana sa ran za a fitar da wani tsari na siyasa kafin karshen shekara".
"Ba za a yi ba a rana ɗaya, amma aikin kwana huɗu na aiki manufa ce da ta dace da tsarin jam'iyyar na sauya tattalin arziki don amfanin ma'aikata da kuma tsarin dabarun jam'iyyar na masana'antu".
Jam'iyyar Labour ba za ta kasance farkon wanda ya goyi bayan irin wannan ra'ayin ba, lokacin da jam'iyyar Green Party ta ba da shawarar yin aiki na kwana hudu a lokacin yakin neman zaben majalisar dokokin kasar na 2017.
Amma, ba a amince da wannan manufar ba a jam'iyyar Labour.
Wani mai magana da yawun jam'iyyar Labour ya ce: "Aiki na kwana huɗu ba manufa ba ce ta jam'iyyar kuma ba a cikin tunanin jam'iyyar ba".
Ministan kudi na makwabcin jam'iyyar Labour John McDonnell ya yi amfani da taron jam'iyyar a makon da ya gabata wajen bayyana shirinsa na kawo sauyi a tattalin arziki na zamantakewa.
McDonnell ya ce ya ƙudura niyyar kwace iko daga hannun "masu zartarwa da ba a san su ba" da kuma "masu cin zarafin" a kamfanonin samar da kayayyaki.
Shirin mai kula da kudaden shiga na Shadow Finance ya kuma jefa shakku kan ko masu hannun jarin kamfanonin samar da ruwa na yanzu za su dawo da kudaden su, yayin da gwamnatin da ke karkashin jagorancin Labour za ta iya "ba su izini" saboda ayyukan rashin mutunci.
Ya kuma tabbatar da shirin samun ma'aikata a kan kwamitocin kamfanoni da kuma kafa asusun mallakar da ya hada da masu mallakar da za su raba kashi 10 cikin 100 na darajar hannun jari na kamfanoni masu zaman kansu ga ma'aikatan da za su samu har zuwa £500 a shekara.
Lindsey Graham da John Kennedy sun gaya wa 60 Minutes cewa binciken da FBI ke yi game da Kavanaugh zai iya canja muryarsu
Binciken da FBI ke yi game da zargin da ake yi wa mai shari'a Brett Kavanaugh ya dage zaben da za a yi na neman shi a babban kotun da akalla mako guda, kuma hakan ya sa ana tambayar ko binciken da FBI ta yi zai sa 'yan majalisar da ke goyon bayan Republican su janye goyon bayansu.
A wata hira da aka yi da 'yan jaridar 60 Minutes a ranar Lahadi, Scott Pelley ya tambayi 'yan majalisa na Republican, John Kennedy da Lindsey Graham, ko hukumar bincike ta FBI za ta iya gano wani abu da zai sa su canja ra'ayinsu.
Kennedy ya fi abokinsa na South Carolina yarda da wannan ra'ayin.
"Hakika", in ji Kennedy.
"Lokacin da na shiga cikin wannan zaman, na ce na yi magana da Alƙali Kavanaugh.
Na kira shi bayan wannan ya faru - bayan zargin ya fito - kuma na ce, "Shin kun yi haka?"
"Ya kasance mai tsananin ƙarfi, mai ƙuduri da kuma tabbatacce".
Amma, kamar dai muryar Graham tana da ƙarfi sosai.
"Na yanke shawara game da Brett Kavanaugh, kuma wani abu zai bukaci zargi mai tsanani", in ji shi.
"Dr. Ford, ban san abin da ya faru ba, amma na san cewa Brett ya musanta hakan sosai", Graham ya kara da cewa, yana nufin Christine Blasey Ford.
"Babu wani daga cikin mutanen da ta ambata da ya tabbatar da hakan.
Hakan ya faru shekaru 36 da suka shige.
Ba na ganin hakan zai canja kome".
Menene bikin Global Citizens, kuma ya yi wani abu wajen rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar, birnin New York zai karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizens Festival  wani bikin kiɗa na shekara-shekara da ke da manyan masu fasaha da kuma babban burin kawar da talauci a duniya.
A karo na bakwai, bikin Global Citizens zai yi maraba da dubban mutane a babban filin wasa na Central Park, inda za su yi kallo tare da Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes, kuma ya kamata ya jawo hankali ga ainihin burin, wato kawar da talauci ta matsananciyar talauci a shekarar 2030.
An fara bikin Global Citizen a shekarar 2012 kuma ya kasance wani fadada na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya ce ta kasa da kasa da ke kokarin kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan masu adawa da talauci.
Don a samu tikiti kyauta zuwa taron (idan ba za a biya kuɗin tikiti na VIP ba), masu halartar za su yi wasu ayyuka ko kuma "aiki", kamar su ba da kai, rubuta wasiƙa ga wani shugaban duniya, yin waya, ko kuma wani aiki mai ma'ana da zai iya jawo hankali game da makasudin kawar da talauci.
Amma yaya nasarar da Global Citizen ta samu, yanzu da suka rage shekaru 12 su cika burinsu?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta ga mutane da yin wasa kyauta yana kawo canji ne, ko kuwa wani abu ne da ake kira "clicktivism"  wato mutane suna jin cewa suna kawo canji ta hanyar sanya hannu a kan wani shafin yanar gizo ko kuma yin wani abu a Twitter?
Global Citizen ta ce tun shekara ta 2011 sun yi rikodin fiye da 'aiki' miliyan 19 da mambobinsu suka yi da suka shafi manufofi daban-daban.
Sun ce waɗannan ayyuka sun sa shugabannin duniya su kafa manufofi da manufofin da suka fi na biliyan 37 da za su shafi mutane biliyan 2.25 a shekara ta 2030.
A farkon 2018, kungiyar ta lissafa manufofi da matakai 390 da suka zama gaskiya sakamakon ayyukansu, wanda ya kai sama da dala biliyan 10 da aka riga aka biya ko aka tara.
Ƙungiyar ta kimanta cewa waɗannan tanadi sun shafi mutane kusan miliyan 649 a dukan duniya.
Daya daga cikin manyan manufofin shine The Power of Nutrition, wanda aka fara a Ingila, haɗin gwiwar masu zuba jari da masu kasuwanci, suna ƙoƙari su "taimaki yara su cika ikonsu" kuma sun yi alkawarin dala miliyan 35 don magance matsalar abinci mai gina jiki a Rwanda bayan sun karbi tweets sama da 4,700 daga Global Citizens.
"Tare da taimakon gwamnatin Ingila, masu bayar da agaji, gwamnatocin wasu ƙasashe, da kuma 'yan ƙasa na duniya kamar ku, rashin cin abinci mai gina jiki zai iya zama sanadin tarihin", in ji Tracey Ullman, jakadan The Power of Nutrition, ga masu sauraro a wani taro a London a watan Afrilu na 2018.
Ƙungiyar ta kuma ce gwamnatin Ingila ta yi alkawarin ba da tallafi don inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga mata da yara bayan ta samu fiye da gayyata 5,000 a kan layi. Wannan aikin, Power of Nutrition, zai taimaka wa mata da yara miliyan biyar da shawara game da abinci mai gina jiki.
