Amurka na iya amfani da rundunar sojan ruwa ta "hana" fitar da makamashin Rasha, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka
"Idan ya zama dole", Washington za ta iya amfani da rundunar sojan ruwa ta Amurka don hana makamashin Rasha shiga kasuwa, har ma a yankin Gabas ta Tsakiya, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka, Ryan Zinke, ga jaridar Washington Examiner.
Zinke ya yi ikirarin cewa, tsoma bakin Rasha a Syria  musamman inda suke aiki bisa gayyatar gwamnatin da ke da hakkin doka  wata hujja ce ta fadada sayar da makamashin su.
"Ina ganin suna cikin Gabas ta Tsakiya ne domin suna son su sayar da makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a gabashin Turai da kuma kudancin Turai", in ji shi.
