Elizabeth Warren "tana tunanin sosai" ta tsaya takarar shugaban kasa a 2020, in ji Sanata daga Massachusetts
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts "tana mai da hankali sosai" kan tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben da aka yi a tsakiyar shekara, in ji ta a ranar Asabar.
