Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da yin amfani da hanyoyin da ba su dace ba da kuma tallar farfaganda
Mako guda bayan wata jaridar kasar Sin ta buga wani shafi na hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke yabawa amfanin hadin gwiwar Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
A ranar Laraba, shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana game da yadda jaridar China Daily ta biya kudin shiga a cikin Des Moines Register  jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a Iowa  bayan da ya zargi kasar Sin da tsoma baki a zaben da aka yi a ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba.
Jami'an Amurka sun shaida wa Reuters cewa zargin da Trump ya yi na sa baki a zaben Amurka na nuna sabon mataki a yakin neman matsin lamba da Washington ke yi kan kasar Sin.
Ko da yake al'ada ce gwamnatoci na ƙasashen waje su yi talla don su inganta kasuwanci, yanzu haka Beijing da Washington suna cikin yaƙin cinikayya da ke ƙaruwa, inda suka yi ta ɗora haraji a kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa da su.
An yi hasashen cewa, sakamakon harajin da kasar Sin ta yi a yakin cinikayya, zai shafi masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa, da ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana na kasar Sin da na Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China, tsohon gwamnan Iowa na tsawon shekaru, wanda babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona ne ga kasar Sin, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
A cikin wani labari da ya fito a jaridar Des Moines Register ta ranar Lahadi, Branstad ya rubuta cewa, "China tana ƙara yin amfani da miyagun hanyoyi ta wajen yin tallace-tallace a cikin jaridarmu mai 'yanci".
"Ta wajen yaɗa farfaganda, gwamnatin Sin tana amfani da al'adar 'yancin magana da 'yancin 'yan jarida na Amirka ta wajen aika da tallace-tallace a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register", in ji Branstad.
"A cikin kantunan sayar da kayayyaki a nan birnin Beijing, za ka ga 'yan muryoyin saɓani kaɗan, kuma ba za ka sami cikakken bayani game da ra'ayoyin mutanen Sin game da yanayin tattalin arzikin China ba, domin kafofin watsa labarai suna ƙarƙashin iko na jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Ya ƙara da cewa "ɗaya daga cikin manyan jaridu na kasar Sin ta ƙi buga" labarinsa, ko da yake bai faɗi ko wane ne ba.
'Yan Republican sun yi watsi da mata kafin zaben tsakiyar shekara, saboda Kavanaugh, manazarta sun gargadi
Yayin da manyan 'yan jam'iyyar Republican ke goyon bayan da kuma kare dan takarar majalisar koli Brett Kavanaugh kan zargin cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za su fuskanci wani mummunan sakamako a zaben da ke tafe, musamman daga mata.
Wannan lamari ya sa mutane suka fara jin haushin, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun bayyana cewa suna son a ci gaba da zaben.
"Ba za a iya canja wannan ba", in ji Grant Reher, farfesa a fannin siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell ta Jami'ar Syracuse, a wata jarida da aka wallafa a The Hill a ranar Asabar.
Reher ya ce yana shakkar cewa bukatar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya yi na gudanar da bincike na FBI a sa'a 11 zai rage fushin masu jefa kuri'a.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba  ba za su manta da shi ba gobe ko a watan Nuwamba", in ji Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara kuma mai magana da yawun ƙungiyar ci gaba ta MoveOn, kamar yadda The Hill ta ruwaito a ranar Juma'a.
A safiyar Juma'a, masu zanga-zanga a wani gangamin majalisar dattawa sun yi ihu suna cewa, "Nuwamba na zuwa!" yayin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a suka zabi ci gaba da zaben Kavanaugh duk da shaidar Farfesa Christine Blasey Ford, in ji Mic.
"Himma da himmar dimokradiyya za su kai wani sabon matsayi", in ji Stu Rothenberg, mai sharhi kan siyasa mai zaman kansa.
"Mutane suna cewa ya riga ya kai wani matsayi mai girma; gaskiya ne.
Amma za ta iya ƙaruwa, musamman tsakanin mata masu zaɓe a cikin birane da kuma matasa masu zaɓe  masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29  waɗanda ba sa yawan jefa ƙuri'a, duk da cewa ba sa son shugaban ƙasa".
Tun kafin Ford ya bayyana zargin cin zarafin dan takarar da ya yi wa shugaban kasa, manazarta sun ce idan 'yan Republican suka ci gaba da takarar za su yi tawaye.
"Ya zama matsala mafi muni ga 'yan Republican", in ji Michael Steele, tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican National, a farkon makon da ya gabata, kamar yadda NBC News ta ruwaito.
"Ba wai kawai batun kuri'ar kwamitin ba ne ko kuma sakamakon karshe ko kuma ko za a hukunta Kavanaugh; amma kuma game da yadda 'yan Republican suka bi da wannan lamarin da kuma yadda suka bi da ita", in ji Guy Cecil, shugaban kungiyar Priorities USA , wata kungiya da ke goyon bayan 'yan Democrat da za a zabe  ga tashar labarai.
Amma jama'ar Amirka sun nuna bambanci game da wanda za su yarda da shi bayan shaidun Ford da Kavanaugh, wanda na biyun ya fi na wasu.
Wani sabon zabe da YouGov ya gudanar ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin 100 na masu amsa sun yi imani da shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35 cikin 100 suka ce sun yi imani da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce sun yi imanin cewa Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya ko kuma ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da yake shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari suka ce haka ne game da Ford.
Bayan da Flake ya ce a yi haka, FBI tana binciken zargin da Ford da kuma wani mutum suka yi, in ji Deborah Ramirez a jaridar The Guardian.
A makon da ya gabata, Ford ya shaida wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade a lokacin da ta ke 'yar shekara 17.
Ramirez ta ce wanda aka naɗa ya nuna mata al'aurarsa a wani biki da aka yi a lokacin da suke karatu a Yale a shekara ta 1980.
Wanda ya kirkiro intanet yana shirin sake gina intanet domin ya yi gogayya da Google da Facebook
Wanda ya kirkiro intanet, Tim Berners-Lee, ya kaddamar da wani sabon kamfani da zai yi gogayya da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Sabon aikin da wannan ƙwararren masanin fasaha ya yi shi ne Inrupt, wani kamfani da ke gina kan dandalin open source na Berners-Lee mai suna Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda ake adana bayanan su da kuma wanda zai iya samun damar waɗanne bayanai.
A wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners Lee ya yi wa dariya cewa shirin Inrupt na nufin "mulkin duniya".
"Dole ne mu yi shi yanzu", in ji shi game da fara kasuwanci.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Aikin yana amfani da fasahar Solid don mutane su iya yin nasu "takarda na kan layi na sirri" ko kuma POD.
Yana iya ƙunsar jerin lambobin sadarwa, abubuwan da za a yi, kalandarku, ɗakunan kiɗa, da wasu kayan aiki na sirri da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify suna cikin burauzar yanar gizo guda a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke na musamman game da tattara bayanan sirri ta hanyar yanar gizo shi ne cewa yana da cikakken ikon mai amfani ya yanke shawarar wanda zai iya samun damar wannan takamaiman bayanin.
Kamfanin ya kira shi "karfafa mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar shugaban kamfanin, John Bruce, manufar Inrupt ita ce hada albarkatu, aiyuka da iyawa don samar da Solid ga kowa.
Kamfanin yanzu ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandalin tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka software a kan kwangilar kwangila da kuma ƙungiyar masu shirye-shiryen sa kai.
Daga wannan makon, masu fasahar kere-kere a duk duniya za su iya gina nasu aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta hanyar amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin shafin yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba sa magana da "Facebook ko Google game da ko za su sauya duk abin da ya faru, don haka duk tsarin kasuwancin su ba zato ba tsammani ya zama mara amfani".
"Ba ma neman izininsu".
A wani rubutu a kan Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "umurnin Inrupt shi ne samar da makamashi na kasuwanci da kuma tsarin halittu da zai iya tabbatar da mutunci da ingancin sabuwar intanet da ake gina a kan Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canja hanyar sadarwa ta intanet sa'ad da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai magana a ji a cikin abin da ake kira muhawara ta tsaka-tsakin intanet.
Yayin da aka kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai ci gaba da kasancewa mai kirkiro da kuma daraktan World Wide Web Consortium, Gidauniyar Yanar gizo da kuma Cibiyar Bayanai ta Bude.
"Ina da kyakkyawan fata game da zamanin Intanet mai zuwa", in ji Berners-Lee.
Bernard Vann: An yi wa wanda ya karɓi Victoria Cross a Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya girmamawa
An yi bikin bikin bikin bikin bikin shekara 100 bayan da wani limamin Cocin Ingila ya lashe lambar yabo ta Victoria Cross a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya.
Lt. Col. kuma Firist Bernard Wann ya lashe wannan umarni a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, a lokacin harin da aka kai a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Amma, wani ɗan bindiga ya kashe shi bayan kwana huɗu, kuma ba a taɓa saninsa ba cewa ya sami lambar yabo mafi girma a ƙasar Ingila.
A ranar Asabar, an bayyana wani abin tunawa da jikokinsa biyu suka yi a wani biki a Rushden, Northamptonshire.
Michael Vann, ɗaya daga cikin jikokinsa, ya ce "ainihin alama ce" cewa an fallasa dutsen daidai shekara 100 bayan nasarar da kakansa ya yi.
A ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Lt. Col. Vann ya ja-goranci rundunarsa a kan Canal de Saint-Quentin "cikin hazo mai-zafi, da kuma harsashin bindiga da kuma bindigogi masu ƙarfi", in ji jaridar London Gazette.
Daga baya, ya gudu zuwa gaban yaƙi, ya ja-goranci mutanensa da "ƙarfin zuciya" kafin ya kai hari ga wani rukunin sojan soja shi kaɗai, ya kashe bindigogi uku.
