Trump ya yi ganawa da shugaban kasar Panama Juan Carlos Varela a watan Yunin 2017 kuma ya yi masa masaukin otal a Panama har sai abokansa suka kori shugabancin Trump.
Jami'an ma'aikatar harkokin wajen Amurka sun yanke shawarar janye manyan jami'an diplomasiyar Amurka daga El Salvador, Jamhuriyar Dominica da Panama bayan "ƙudurin da aka yi kwanan nan na daina amincewa da Taiwan", in ji Heather Nauert, mai magana da yawun ma'aikatar harkokin wajen Amurka a cikin wata sanarwa a farkon watan.
Amma El Salvador ne kawai aka hukunta, kuma sun samu kimanin dala miliyan 140 daga Amurka a shekarar 2017 don sarrafa miyagun kwayoyi, ci gaba da tallafi.
Hukuncin da aka gabatar, wanda ya haɗa da yanke taimakon kuɗi da ƙuntatawa a kan izinin shiga, zai kasance mai raɗaɗi ga ƙasar ta Amurka ta Tsakiya da ke da yawan rashin aikin yi da kuma yawan kisan kai.
Yayin da tarurrukan cikin gida suka ci gaba, jami'an Amurka ta Arewa da ta Tsakiya sun dage wani babban taro kan tsaro da ci gaban tattalin arziki, wanda ya ci gaba da taron da aka yi a bara, wanda ake ganin mataki ne na hana bakin haure shiga Amurka.
Amma a tsakiyar watan Satumba, manyan jami'ai sun bayyana cewa suna son a yi taron duk da haka, kuma hakan ya sa suka daina yin la'akari da hukunta El Salvador.
Mataimakin shugaban kasa Mike Pence zai yi jawabi a taron da aka shirya a tsakiyar watan Oktoba domin nuna muhimmancin da Amurkawa ke ba wa taron, in ji jami'an diplomasiyya.
Kuma wakilai uku na Amirka sun koma ƙasar El Salvador da Panama da kuma Jamhuriyar Dominica a ɓoye ba tare da wani sabon hukunci ko takunkumi daga Washington ba.
