'Yar jam'iyyar Brexit, Andrea Jenkyns, ta halarci zanga-zangar kuma ta gaya wa manema labarai cewa: "Ina gaya muku: Firayim Minista, ku saurari mutane.
"Tsarin Chequers ba shi da kyau a cikin jama'a, 'yan adawa ba su amince da shi ba, ba shi da kyau a cikin jam'iyyarmu da kuma tsakanin masu fafutukarmu, waɗanda a zahiri suna kan titi suna sa mu zaɓe.
